page.title: 14A Day In My Life
page.content: I usually wake up about half past seven every morning.I do some reading before I get out of bed then I get dressed.After that I go into the bathroom,clean my teeth,and wash my face.Then I go down into the bar of our public house.I brush my hair,eat my breakfast and put everything on for school.I leave home at about ten to nine and then go into school at nine o'clock.My favourite subjects are maths,English,and sewing.I come out of school at quarter past three and go home.Afterwards I have a packet of crisps and a can of Coca Cola.Then I watch T.V.I go to bed between nine and ten o'clock and get to sleep about an hour after. by Sara_Jane Edwards Age 9
